Edit Interaction between background and chart, Formatting selection and Chart title 21

 


-        Select Any Area Chart from the selection  > Format> Edit Interaction

-        Check all other 11 background shape beside the background shape of that measures background shape None

-        Click on edit interaction to save it

 

Select Each area chart visuals from selection and Repeat this process to all 12 measures area chart.



Manage the selection of the visuals

-        We want to keep the dynamic background shape behind the are chart, therefore we are going to manage selection here

-        GO to the insert > selection > select all shape created for background > from the down aero put them under the area visual Bus Passenger> save it

Format

         Line = on > line color = ( grey)

        Title > on > Title Text = Entries per Day by Entry Type, Font Color=, Background = , Alignment= Middle   Text Size = 11,                     Font   Family = Segoe (Bold), transparency = 30%

         Background > On >transparency = 30%
